软件包 org.biosino.CHS.image

接口摘要
Rendering The interface represents objects to be rendered, regardless of the graphic device.
Wrapper The interface represents graphic devices that can render a Rendering object.
 

类摘要
ChrCHSRendering The class renders all CHS between a center chromosome and other surrounding chromosomes.
ChrRendering This class renders a chromosome, which is used to compare CHS between chromosomes.
CHSRendering This class is used to render a CHS object, which contains two GenoLocRendering objects.
GenoLocRendering This class is used to render a GenoLoc object,which is an half part of a CHS rendering.
ImageWrapper Wrap an image using bitmap format.
LPAlg This class is used to caculate the locations for gene labels given the locations of genes.
PsWrapper Wrap an image using post script format (vector map).
StringRendering This class is used to control the location of string drawing.
